text: Landesbank Baden, short for Landesbank Baden-Wurttemberg (LBBW) is a full- service commercial bank and parent company of three commercial banks (SudwestLB, Landesgirokasse, and the commercial banking business of L-Bank) and the Landesbank for the Federal States Baden-WÃ¼rttemberg, Rhineland- Palatinate and Saxony.
